Class SimpleEdge

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Edge
      • model.SimpleEdge

  • public class SimpleEdge
extends Edge
    This is a class for SimpleEdge which extends the class Edge. A SimpleEdge object is an edge which has exactly one start node and one end node and has no label.
